videos.description: DeShone Kizer hits Equanimeous St. Brown who takes it the rest of the way for a 79-yard Notre Dame touchdown on the first play from scrimmage.
videos.headline: Irish strike on first play of game

videos.description: Eric Dungey run for 3 yds for a TD
videos.headline: E. Dungey run for 3 yds for a TD

videos.description: Notre Dame blocks Syracuse's extra point attempt and Cole Luke returns it to the end zone for two points.
videos.headline: Notre Dame returns blocked extra point for two

videos.description: Notre Dame QB DeShone Kizer finds Equanimeous St. Brown for his second touchdown of the game, this one going for 67 yards.
videos.headline: Kizer and Brown connect on second long TD

videos.description: Syracuse responds to two long Notre Dame touchdowns with Amba Etta-Tawo hauling in a 72-yard TD for the Orange.
videos.headline: Syracuse answers with 72-yard TD

videos.description: C.J. Sanders returns the Syracuse kickoff 92 yards for a touchdown to put the Irish ahead of the Orange 23-13.
videos.headline: Notre Dame returns Syracuse kick 92 yards for TD

videos.description: Notre Dame's Devin Studstill ejected for targeting, initiated by replay official
videos.headline: Notre Dame's Devin Studstill ejected for targeting, initiated by replay official

videos.description: Eric Dungey pass complete to Steve Ishmael for 35 yds to the NDame 8 for a 1ST down
videos.headline: E. Dungey pass to S. Ishmael for 35 yds

videos.description: Syracuse QB Eric Dungey sneaks it in on 4th and goal to narrow Notre Dame's lead to three points.
videos.headline: Syracuse capitalizes on 4th and goal

videos.description: Notre Dame WR Josh Adams attempts to hurdle a Syracuse defender during his 44-yard reception.
videos.headline: Notre Dame WR makes crazy hurdle attempt

videos.description: DeShone Kizer runs it in for a 3-yard touchdown to give Notre Dame a 10-point lead on Syracuse.
videos.headline: Kizer walks in for 3-yard TD

videos.description: Notre Dame and Syracuse combined for 36 points and five touchdowns in the first five minutes of Saturday's game.

videos.headline: D. Kizer pass intercepted by Z. Franklin

videos.description: DeShone Kizer connects with a wide open Kevin Stepherson for a 54-yard touchdown to give Notre Dame a 40-27 lead over Syracuse.
videos.headline: Kizer throws third TD of the game of over 50 yards
